ue to COVID-19. We have been open and transparent about the measures we have been providing to support families, businesses and workers. Even our health care&#10;Speaker: The Chair&#10;Content: We'll go back to Mr. Williamson.&#10;Speaker: Mr. John Williamson&#10;Content: Except you have not. The Auditor General is underfunded. We have no idea about">
