conomies.&#10;3) Minister Fortier emphasizes the government's commitment to transparency and supporting Canadians but has not given a clear reason or timeline for when an economic projection may be provided. The opposition parties argue that the government's refusal to provide an update is a sign of a lack of transparency and accountability.">
